results.name: Engineering Library - Collaborative Space
results.description: The Engineering Library is based on the first floor of the Department of Engineering main site on Trumpington Street. The Library's Collaborative Space is ideal for group study with large, round tables, window-facing seating, sit-stand desk spaces, a multi-use study break area, a staffed Information point for enquiries, and a self-service borrowing machine.
results.address:
Department of Engineering
Trumpington Street
Cambridge CB2 1PZ
results.floor: First Floor of the Baker Building
results.restriction: Monday-Friday: Doors: 09:00-17:00 | Information Desk: 10:00-16:00 | Other times: Department-approved card access (e,g, Engineering undergraduates have access from 08:00 to 19:00 every day)
